# Keep the Lambda build context (deploy/Dockerfile.lambda, context = repo root)
# minimal and hash-stable. The Dockerfile only COPYs pyproject.toml, src/,
# configs/, corpus/, models/cloud_artifacts/, and models/audio_bank/ - exclude
# everything else, especially the 114MB LoRA adapter under models/, the venv,
# node_modules, datasets, and results.
*
!pyproject.toml
!src
!configs
!corpus
!models
models/*
!models/cloud_artifacts
!models/audio_bank
!deploy
